The language code of this Locale instance. [Read-Only]  <pre>
 var locale:Locale = new Locale(&quot;en_US_MAC&quot;);
 trace(locale.language); // outputs &quot;en&quot;
 </pre>

The country code of this Locale instance. [Read-Only]  <pre>
 var locale:Locale = new Locale(&quot;en_US_MAC&quot;);
 trace(locale.country); // outputs &quot;US&quot;
 </pre>

The variant part of this Locale instance. [Read-Only]  <pre>
 var locale:Locale = new Locale(&quot;en_US_MAC&quot;);
 trace(locale.variant); // outputs &quot;MAC&quot;
 </pre>

Returns the locale String that was used to construct this Locale instance. For example:  <pre>
 var locale:Locale = new Locale(&quot;en_US_MAC&quot;);
 trace(locale.toString()); // outputs &quot;en_US_MAC&quot;
 </pre>  construct this Locale instance.
